        public void setFilter(IOLocationFilter filter)
        This filter may be used by renderers to show unsupported locations as disabled. (For example, see the BasicTileCellRenderer.)

        Note this does not actually filter elements out of this list, for that you need to call: IOLocationFilter.filter(srcList)
